column5: Well, got too much time on my hands today as my homework was done, and didn't get to go out fishing on such a beautiful night, so I'm online browsing fishing stuff...Great thing is, I stumbled onto this video where I found of Dave Mercer.  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1-affiREbKI&feature=player_embedded  Cheers!
LOL, way to get him Dave.
